y Ukrainian brand of household chemicals, was founded in 2004. During its existence, it has been repeatedly awarded with various awards:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>2006 - Diploma of the Laureate according to the results of the 4th All-Ukrainian competition of product quality \\"100 best goods of Ukraine 2006-2007\\", which earned an indispensable tool for cleaning stoves - \\"Means for dissolving dirt, grease, soot \\"MILAM\\"<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>2007 - GOLD MEDAL and WINNER\'S DIPLOMA of the national business - rating KVED 24.51 for the main activity \\"Production of soap and detergents, cleaning and polishing products\\", with the title of LEADER OF THE INDUSTRY 2008<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>2008 \\u2013 Order of the 1st degree \\"Star of the Ukrainian Economy\\" for a significant contribution to the development of the Ukrainian economy<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>2009\\u00a0\\u2013 Diploma of the finalist according to the results of the competition \\"100 Best Goods of Ukraine - 2009\\" at the regional level, for the highly demanded and popular \\"Means for removing stains\\" MILAM \\"<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>2010\\u00a0\\u2013 Diploma of the winner according to the results of the competition \\"100 Best Goods of Ukraine - 2010\\" at the national level, received \\"Sanitary-hygienic product\\" Santri-MILAM gel \\"<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>The best combination of price and quality made the Trademark one of the leaders in the industry and rand adheres to this course to this day.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A rich assortment of products is represented by both classic products, such as: \\"BELIZNA MILAM\\", \\"SANTRI\\", \\"SANTRI MILAM GEL\\" and \\"KROT\\", as well as completely new positions.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The brand does not stand still, it improves existing positions and develops new directions presented under the trade mark \\"MILAM CHEMICAL\\".<\\/p>"},{"name":"\\u0418\\u0437\\u043e\\u0431\\u0440\\u0430\\u0436\\u0435\\u043d\\u0438\\u0435 1 \\u0432\\u0442\\u043e\\u0440\\u043e\\u0433\\u04