            array('id' => '2191','field' => 'description','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Flavored liquid stain remover "MILAM CHEMICAL". Removes stains from sauces, coffee, wine, berries, blood, etc. from delicate fabrics. Does not damage fibers. An effective oxygen additive to conventional washing powder.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '1','created_at' => '2022-08-15 14:10:54','updated_at' => '2022-08-15 14:10:54'),
            array('id' => '2192','field' => 'instructions','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Suitable for all types of fabrics. Retains color and does not damage product fibers. <strong>Does not contain chlorine.</strong> Shake the contents of the vial before use. Using a spray bottle, apply the product to the stain in the form of foam. Leave for 5-15 min. depending on pollution. Carry out washing as indicated in the product recommendations. If necessary, add 100-150 ml of product to the washing machine. Before using the product, carefully read all warnings on the product, pay attention to the washing instructions. For fabrics with unstable dyes, first test the stain remover on an inconspicuous area. Spray onto soiled collar, cuffs or other surface. Place in the washing machine and wash in the usual way no later than 10 minutes after spraying. Do not let the product dry on the fabric. Can be used for all types of washing. Has a disinfecting effect. Eliminates bad smell.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '1','created_at' => '2022-08-15 14:10:54','updated_at' => '2022-08-15 14:10:54'),
            array('id' => '2193','field' => 'security','language' => 'en','value' => '<p><strong>Carefully!</strong> Contains hydrogen peroxide! Wear rubber gloves for prolonged use. Take care of your eyes. Use as directed. Do not point sprayer at eyes. In case of contact with eyes or skin, rinse with running water. Keep tightly closed and out of the reach of children. Do not apply to metal parts of clothing. Afraid of the heat. Do not store in direct sunlight. Do not pour into another container.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '1','created_at' => '2022-08-15 14:10:54','updated_at' => '2022-08-15 14:10:54'),
            array('id' => '2194','field' => 'compound','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Water, hydrogen peroxide (&lt;5%), nonionic surfactants (&lt;5%), anionic surfactants (&lt;5%), sodium tripolyphosphate (&lt;5%), trilon B (&lt;5%), orthophosphoric acid, perfume, preservative.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '1','created_at' => '2022-08-15 14:10:54','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 17:58:17'),
