            array('id' => '2529','field' => 'security','language' => 'en','value' => '<p><strong>Carefully! Contains acid!!!</strong><span> Do not point the sprayer at people\'s faces. Do not breathe vapors when spraying the product. In case of contact with eyes or skin, rinse with running water. Use rubber gloves. Keep tightly closed, out of the reach of children. Do not mix with other agents. Afraid of heat. Do not store in direct sunlight. The product freezes, after defrosting it retains its properties. Use as directed.</span></p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '26','created_at' => '2022-08-18 10:38:45','updated_at' => '2022-08-23 11:24:57'),
