            array('id' => '2545','field' => 'description','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>The product is designed to give shine to hard surfaces, creates a water-repellent effect to remove surface contaminants with varnish, paint, plastic or any other coating, as well as to aromatize and deodorize the air.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '44','created_at' => '2022-08-18 13:12:43','updated_at' => '2022-08-18 13:12:43'),
            array('id' => '2546','field' => 'instructions','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Spray the product on the surface and rub thoroughly with a soft, dry cloth to a shine. For surfaces laminated with paper or unstable material, painted or varnished, it is necessary to test the agent on an inconspicuous area.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '44','created_at' => '2022-08-18 13:12:43','updated_at' => '2022-08-18 13:12:43'),
            array('id' => '2547','field' => 'security','language' => 'en','value' => '<p><strong>Check fuse! Do not point sprayer at eyes!</strong> Use as directed. Before use, you must read the instructions for surface treatment with this product. It is recommended to test on an inconspicuous area before use. Dangerous for the eyes! Work with rubber gloves. In case of contact with skin and eyes, rinse thoroughly with plenty of water. Keep tightly closed and out of the reach of children. Do not mix with other agents.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '44','created_at' => '2022-08-18 13:12:43','updated_at' => '2022-08-18 13:12:43'),
            array('id' => '2548','field' => 'compound','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Water, organic solvent, non-ionic surfactants&lt;5%, cationic surfactants&lt;5%, preservative, perfume.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '44','created_at' => '2022-08-18 13:12:43','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 16:26:22'),
