            array('id' => '2644','field' => 'description','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>The product is designed to give shine to hard surfaces, creates a water-repellent effect to remove surface contaminants with varnish, paint, plastic or any other coating, as well as to aromatize and deodorize the air.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '54','created_at' => '2022-08-19 12:29:18','updated_at' => '2022-08-19 12:29:18'),
            array('id' => '2645','field' => 'instructions','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Dissolve 50-100 ml of the product in 5 liters of water. Use a sponge or rag to wipe the contaminated surface with the solution. For heavily soiled surfaces, apply undiluted product to a sponge or surface and rub thoroughly.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '54','created_at' => '2022-08-19 12:29:18','updated_at' => '2022-08-19 12:29:18'),
            array('id' => '2646','field' => 'security','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Use as directed. Before use, you must read the instructions for surface treatment with this product. It is recommended to test on an inconspicuous area before use. Dangerous for the eyes! Work with rubber gloves. In case of contact with skin and eyes, rinse thoroughly with plenty of water. Keep tightly closed and out of the reach of children. Do not mix with other agents.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '54','created_at' => '2022-08-19 12:29:18','updated_at' => '2022-08-19 12:29:18'),
            array('id' => '2647','field' => 'compound','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Water, mixture of wax and polymers, anionic surfactants &lt;5%, organic solvents, nonionic surfactants &lt;5%, Trilon B, glycerin, preservative, perfume.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '54','created_at' => '2022-08-19 12:29:18','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 16:17:41'),
