            array('id' => '2925','field' => 'description','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Means It is intended for cleaning and disinfection of all surfaces in the kitchen, in the bathroom, in the bathroom.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '45','created_at' => '2022-08-20 11:36:36','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 11:36:36'),
            array('id' => '2926','field' => 'instructions','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Apply the powder to a damp sponge, rub the surface and rinse with water. To remove old dirt and stains, apply the powder directly to a damp surface, leave for 3-5 minutes, rub and rinse with water.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '45','created_at' => '2022-08-20 11:36:36','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 11:36:36'),
            array('id' => '2927','field' => 'security','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Store separately from foodstuffs. The product is not intended for washing vegetables and other food products. Keep out of reach of children. Take care of your eyes! In case of contact with skin or eyes, rinse thoroughly with plenty of water. Seek medical attention if necessary. If swallowed, seek medical advice immediately and provide container or label. Do not mix with other cleaning agents. Store in places protected from moisture and heating devices.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '45','created_at' => '2022-08-20 11:36:36','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 11:36:36'),
