            array('id' => '2934','field' => 'description','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Designed for multifunctional use: as an additive to the main detergent for washing heavily soiled linen, overalls, table linen and bed linen, it hygienically cleans and removes unpleasant odors. It can be used together with detergents and cleaners.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '27','created_at' => '2022-08-20 11:45:37','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 11:45:37'),
            array('id' => '2935','field' => 'instructions','language' => 'en','value' => '<p><strong>Washing in the washing machine:</strong> 3 tbsp. put spoons into the <span>barrel</span> of the washing machine. Wash at 50-100°C. To soften water, add 2-3 tbsp. spoons in the washing machine <span>barrel</span>. At the same time, reduce the amount of detergent used.</p>
<p><strong>Hand wash:</strong> For more effective detergent or soap, add 3 tbsp. tablespoons of soda per 10 liters of water.</p>
<p><strong>Caution!</strong> do not use soda when washing clothes with a special coating or membrane surface, wool, delicate fabrics.</p>
<p><strong>Cleaning kitchen surfaces:</strong> wipe the contaminated surface with a sponge moistened with a solution of soda 3 tbsp. spoons for 1 liter of hot water. Then rinse with clean water and wipe dry.</p>
<p><strong>Washing the floor:</strong> to remove dirt from the floor, dilute 3 tbsp. tablespoons of soda in 5 liters of hot water and wash the floor with a soft cloth. Then rinse with clean water and wipe dry.</p>
<p><strong>Caution!</strong> Do not use baking soda on aluminum, wood, brick, lacquered parquet, laminate, painted surfaces, unwaxed floors, lacquered furniture or fiberglass tiles.</p>
<p><strong>Washing dishes:</strong> to remove dirt and grease from dishes, dissolve 3 tbsp. spoons in 1 liter of hot water and wash the dishes with a solution. Then rinse thoroughly with clean water.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '27','created_at' => '2022-08-20 11:45:37','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 11:45:37'),
            array('id' => '2936','field' => 'security','language' => 'en','value' => '<p>Keep out of reach of children. Take care of your eyes! In case of contact with skin or eyes, rinse thoroughly with plenty of water. Seek medical attention if necessary. If swallowed, seek medical advice immediately and provide container or label. Keep away from foodstuffs. Do not mix with other detergents. Store in places protected from moisture and heating devices.</p>','localizable_type' => 'Products','localizable_id' => '27','created_at' => '2022-08-20 11:45:37','updated_at' => '2022-08-20 11:45:37'),
